snippet.textDisplay:
Chapter 2 fortnite puts us Mobile players up against console and PC. Seriously EPIC, a mobile device, 2 thumbs versus a controller or mouse and keyboard.

I used to love playing this game, but I think it should be noted if you don’t play claw, 4 or more fingers, and have zero ping, and use the latest iPad Pro, you are not going to have fun,,, be prepared to be slaughtered by console and PC.

I don’t know how epic got away with this, I think it’s a big money grab as they have saved a tonne of money by removing our “mobile only” server, and putting everyone together.

Nothing else makes sense, I cannot see how they justified doing this, from over 1000 people surveyed, everyone said it’s UNFAIR, AND DISADVANTAGES MOBILE PLAYERS.

Shame on you EPIC, shame on you.

Apple should ban this game from the App Store.
